import React from 'react';
import{ Menu } from 'semantic-ui-react';

export default ()=>{
    return (
        <Menu>
            <Menu.Item>
                Ethereum X Game
            </Menu.Item>
            <Menu.Menu position="right">
                <Menu.Item>
                    Lottery
                </Menu.Item>
                <Menu.Item>
                    Coin Flip
                </Menu.Item>
                <Menu.Item>
                    Market
                </Menu.Item>

            </Menu.Menu>
        </Menu>
    )
}
